author: J. Edward Moreno
title: California sees deadliest day since beginning of coronavirus outbreak
description: California reported 115 deaths due to coronavirus Wednesday, marking the deadliest 24-hour period since the start of the pandemic in the state.
content:
California reported 115 deaths due to coronavirus Wednesday, marking the deadliest 24-hour period since the start of the pandemic in the state.
